reviewText: I was very impressed with the price of this item and the quality of it for 1. being a VHS and 2. being an old VHS. Brought back childhood memories! It was true to description.

This volume set is great because it contians four full episodes (Pink Spots, Birthday Special, Wish Fairies and Monster Bananas) with a running time of 90 minutes.  My youngest loves it although my 5 yo is less entertained.  I like it because it contains educational messages in a very G-rated context.
